# =========================================================================== #
# .gitignore — deny-all, EXPLICIT allowlist (org ADR-0003, hardened)
# --------------------------------------------------------------------------- #
# `**` ignores everything; every tracked path is then re-included EXPLICITLY
# below. The ONLY glob permitted is the leading `**` — no other wildcards. A
# path is committable only if it is named here, so a stray secret or scratch
# file (e.g. ansible/secrets.yml) can never be swept in by a glob; it simply
# will not be tracked until someone deliberately allowlists it.
#
# Consequence: adding a NEW committed file requires adding its line here. CI's
# `make allowlist-check` fails on a deliverable file that is not allowlisted.
#
# Everything else — compose scripts, `_dev-build/`, lab helpers, `.env`,
# Terraform state, editor/agent tooling — lives on disk, never committed.
# =========================================================================== #

# Ignore everything by default.
**

# --------------------------------------------------------------------------- #
#  Repository root — governance + tooling config.
#  (CONTRIBUTING / CODE_OF_CONDUCT / SECURITY / SUPPORT are inherited org-wide
#   from github.com/nwarila-platform/.github and linked from the README.)
# --------------------------------------------------------------------------- #
!/.ansible-lint
!/.editorconfig
!/.gitattributes
!/.gitignore
!/.pre-commit-config.yaml
!/.release-please-manifest.json
!/.yamllint.yml
!/CHANGELOG.md
!/LICENSE
!/Makefile
!/README.md
!/mkdocs.yml
!/release-please-config.json
!/requirements-dev.txt

# --------------------------------------------------------------------------- #
#  GitHub — CI, the deploy loop, templates, CODEOWNERS, framework pin.
# --------------------------------------------------------------------------- #
!/.github/
!/.github/.framework-pin
!/.github/CODEOWNERS
!/.github/ISSUE_TEMPLATE/
!/.github/ISSUE_TEMPLATE/bug_report.yml
!/.github/ISSUE_TEMPLATE/config.yml
!/.github/ISSUE_TEMPLATE/feature_request.yml
!/.github/dependabot.yml
!/.github/pull_request_template.md
!/.github/workflows/
!/.github/workflows/ci.yml
!/.github/workflows/deploy.yml
!/.github/workflows/release-please.yml
!/.github/workflows/security.yaml

# --------------------------------------------------------------------------- #
#  Documentation (Diátaxis) + ADRs.
# --------------------------------------------------------------------------- #
!/docs/
!/docs/README.md
!/docs/decision-records/
!/docs/decision-records/README.md
!/docs/decision-records/org/
!/docs/decision-records/org/.gitkeep
!/docs/decision-records/repo/
!/docs/decision-records/repo/.gitkeep
!/docs/decision-records/repo/0001-secrets-and-tls.md
!/docs/decision-records/repo/0002-combined-terraform-ansible-delivery.md
!/docs/decision-records/repo/0003-deny-all-explicit-gitignore.md
!/docs/decision-records/template/
!/docs/decision-records/template/.gitkeep
!/docs/explanation/
!/docs/explanation/.gitkeep
!/docs/explanation/architecture.md
!/docs/explanation/composition-model.md
!/docs/explanation/toolchain-rhel8.md
!/docs/how-to/
!/docs/how-to/.gitkeep
!/docs/how-to/deploy-the-stack.md
!/docs/how-to/provide-aws-credentials-safely.md
!/docs/reference/
